Package cs2030s.fp

Class Maybe<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • cs2030s.fp.Maybe<T>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Maybe.None, Maybe.Some
    public abstract class Maybe<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    This abstract class implements an object of Maybe, whereby it could contain an element, "Some" or it could not contain en element, "None".

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Class Description
      static class  Maybe.None
      This class implements a None object, whereby it does not contain anything inside.
      static class  Maybe.Some<T>
      This class implements a Some object, whereby it contains an item of type T inside.
